name: Turning Japanese big bum baby pants - 3m
description:
Cute Japanese girl cotton print trousers with an extra sneaky bit at the back to fit cloth nappies (see that purple linen panel!), they fit great with disposible nappies too! An elasticated waist makes them super easy to get off and on during wiggly nappy change times!

I am happy to design and make custom orders - just ask!

Pattern designed by Rae Hoekstra of made-by-rae.com. I am an authorized seller.

description:
Super easy for the little ones to get into and out of on their own. 
Nice and breezy for a warm day or with a long sleeved top for chillier times. Can be worn as a tunic then a top as your child elongates (as they do!). They will get a good two years wear out of this. It is triple stitched under the arms for active girls. Cotton.

I am happy to design and make custom orders - just ask!
